WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.075
On a perfectly clear night
in Las Vegas ...

00:00:01.284 --> 00:00:05.330
and with the expected crowd
of celebrities and eager sports fans ...

00:00:05.538 --> 00:00:10.501
piling into the MGM Grand, the two
best heavyweights in the world ...

00:00:10.710 --> 00:00:16.674
prepare to meet, after an eight-month
dance, around and toward each other.

